    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 259399.0,
      "end_time": 261159.0,
      "text": "and don’t have term limits."
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 261640.0,
      "end_time": 265120.0,
      "text": "Helmut Kohl is the longest-serving chancellor to-date."
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 265120.0,
      "end_time": 267560.0,
      "text": "He was in office for 16 years."
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 268400.0,
      "end_time": 269760.0,
      "text": "Okay, I know that was a lot,"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 269760.0,
      "end_time": 272840.0,
      "text": "so why even bother with all of this complexity?"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 272840.0,
      "end_time": 275600.0,
      "text": "To understand why, well, we have to"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 275600.0,
      "end_time": 276880.0,
      "text": "look to the history books."
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 276880.0,
      "end_time": 278719.0,
      "text": "Many Germans saw the failure of"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 278720.0,
      "end_time": 280100.0,
      "text": "the Weimar Republic as"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 280100.0,
      "end_time": 281540.0,
      "text": "the failure of the country’s"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 281540.0,
      "end_time": 283980.0,
      "text": "fragmented parliamentary system."
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 283980.0,
      "end_time": 285181.0,
      "text": "After World War II,"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 285181.0,
      "end_time": 287140.0,
      "text": "the Federal Republic of Germany"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 287140.0,
      "end_time": 289580.0,
      "text": "transferred power from the president"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 289600.0,
      "end_time": 290600.0,
      "text": "toward the Bundestag"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 290600.0,
      "end_time": 292420.0,
      "text": "and encouraged political majorities"
    },
